import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, CardMedia } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 4 }}>
      <Box sx={{ my: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" gutterBottom align="center">
          Welcome to ProLearnX
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" align="center" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
          Share and acquire IT skills with a community of like-minded learners
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="140"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random?coding"
              alt="Coding"
            />
            <CardContent>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                Learn Coding
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Explore tutorials, projects, and resources to enhance your coding skills.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="140"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random?cybersecurity"
              alt="Cybersecurity"
            />
            <CardContent>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                Cybersecurity
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Learn about security threats, protection strategies, and secure coding practices.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="140"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random?data"
              alt="Data Science"
            />
            <CardContent>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                Data Science
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Discover the world of data analysis, machine learning, and artificial intelligence.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Home;
